{"tid":574032,"cid":6,"subCid":0,"title":"反雲既人 入一入黎","createTime":"2018-02-27T04:39:32.000Z","updateTime":"2018-02-27T07:07:22.000Z","uid":31314,"like":1,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"401cbe2d7a1e54ef29d7927b93cab660da4b35bc","tid":574032,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T04:39:32.000Z","msg":"見到你地係咁抽雲加水<br />\n我真係越諗越撚灰<br />\n根本唔知自己做乜要支持一個領隊20幾年而換得俾人嘲笑既地步<br />\n知唔知咩叫尊重、respect?<br />\n好撚煩囉成日搬雲加又輸出o黎話點話點<br />\n我心諗一句, 你講既我全部知, 甚至乎你唔知既我都知<br />\n第一唔使你教我<br />\n第二唔使你分析我聽<br />\n第三我無屌你隊愛隊領隊先<br />\n一失分出面最少半版post 係抽水<br />\n好難忍到一個都唔reply<br />\n或者轉去其他forum 係唯一解決方法"},{"pid":"8be114707a6c9d194ee4387a70f0790afb1c007f","tid":574032,"uid":54373,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T04:40:54.000Z","msg":"反雲打丁打到廁紙斷貨<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/27/124026_aaf353778cbe7375e4da9b2e9d1ae1d3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F27%2F124026_aaf353778cbe7375e4da9b2e9d1ae1d3.png&h=4cff6c7d&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"5a057c8eabff7b236ee80c7c8d159eb93f5503b3","tid":574032,"uid":18646,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T04:41:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lny/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8187127b5a156febe3ac68fa97d2c4928a16836d","tid":574032,"uid":31314,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"8be114707a6c9d194ee4387a70f0790afb1c007f","tid":574032,"uid":54373,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-02-27T04:40:54.000Z","msg":"反雲打丁打到廁紙斷貨<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/02/27/124026_aaf353778cbe7375e4da9b2e9d1ae1d3.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F02%2F27%2F124026_aaf353778cbe7375e4da9b2e9d1ae1d3.png&h=4cff6c7d&s={SIZE}\" 